      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Per-query energy across query length, by model</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Per-query energy in watt-hours across short (300-token), medium (1000-token), and long (1500-token) prompts. Each panel is one model. Y-axes are independent per panel — the shape of each line, not its absolute height, conveys how the model scales with prompt length. Models arranged top-left to bottom-right by approximate energy ascending. Coloured by organization. Source: Jegham et al. environmental footprint snapshot (12-model subset).</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
